                    <history>
                        <origin>
                            <origDate/>
                            Both units of the manuscript were copied from the same manuscript, <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/GG00041">ኢሮብ፡, Gunda Gunde, C3-IV-7</ref> from <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0005Gund">Gunda Gunde</placeName>. Another <foreign xml:lang="gez">gadl</foreign> contained in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/GG00041">ኢሮብ፡, Gunda Gunde, C3-IV-7</ref> was copied in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ANLcr89"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: ANLcr89</span></ref>.
                            According to <ref target="#e3"/>, <ref target="#p2"/> was received by <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3182ContiRo">Carlo Conti Rossini</persName>
                            from  
                            ‘<persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14786Talam">Talamonto</persName>, <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC1579Asmara">Asmara</placeName>’ in <date when="1925-03-11" evidence="internal-date">11. 3.
                                1925</date>. A similar origin may be assumed for <ref target="#p1"/>, but is not specified in the catalogue.
                        </origin>
                        <acquisition>The manuscript passed into the possession of the library in <date when="1950">1950</date>, following Conti Rossini’s death in <date when="1949">1949</date> 
                            (see <ref target="https://www.menestrel.fr/?-Roma-&amp;lang=fr#845">Menestrel</ref>).</acquisition>
                    </history>
                    
